            "  C0 vs C2         226    0.0295    0.1768    ns  (means: -0.93 vs -1.71)\n",
            "  C0 vs C3         354    0.1963    1.0000    ns  (means: -0.93 vs -0.78)\n",
            "  C1 vs C2         300    0.0000    0.0000   ***  (means: 0.50 vs -1.71)\n",
            "  C1 vs C3         738    0.0001    0.0005   ***  (means: 0.50 vs -0.78)\n",
